---
title: Ricotta Ravioli in Roasted Butternut Sauce with Spinach and Italian Style Cheese
description: Perfect for autumn, this Ricotta Ravioli in Roasted Butternut Sauce uses seasonal squash in a creamy rosemary sauce for a cosier way to enjoy ravioli.
